page.title: 17A 9 YEAR OLD'S SUNDAY
page.content: 7.00AM Get up and read. 7.10 Watch television. 8.00 Play with the computer. 8.30 Get dressed and wash. 8.31 Have breakfast. 8.35 Play with the computer. 9.00 Watch television. 9.30 Go out in the garden. 9.40 Play the piano. 10.00 Play with the computer. 10.30 Ride my bicycle. 11.00 Play the piano. 11.30 Play in the garden. 11.45 Play with the computer. 12.30PM Have lunch. 1.00 Play on my bicycle. 2.00 Play with my friends. 3.00 Go home.Play with computer. 4.00 Play at my friend's house. 6.00 Go home and have tea. 7.00 Watch television. 9.30 Go to bed. Luke(Age 9).
